    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A town is being bled dry by a hidden cult, and every drop of blood fuels their dark magic. Tear through their ranks before they amass enough blood to usher in a new world order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/5b960df03bc14db80fb3de90583d04e9.poster.avif?t=1755598292\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/5b960df03bc14db80fb3de90583d04e9.webm?t=1755598292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/5b960df03bc14db80fb3de90583d04e9.mp4?t=1755598292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kill Them All</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use each character's unique skill set to slash, stab, punch, and shoot your way through the cult's compounds. Use stealth tactics to get the jump on your enemies, or confront them head on, odds be damned. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dominic, a man with the unique ability to eject blades from his wrists</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Darius, a mage that picks up the blood of fallen foes and uses it to cast devastating magic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demi, a woman who can shoot regenerating spines from her forearms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And many more!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/b205ad426c17352fb10c0bcbfc1ce520.poster.avif?t=1755598292\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/b205ad426c17352fb10c0bcbfc1ce520.webm?t=1755598292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/b205ad426c17352fb10c0bcbfc1ce520.mp4?t=1755598292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging Boss Encounters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See what blood magic is truly capable of! In these unique and varied boss scenarios, use the game's third-person movement mechanics to dodge volleys of projectiles, hide behind cover, and jump over waves of blood, all while trying to aim your own attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/6223572311e4f102e8caa1a1548a0bb6.poster.avif?t=1755598292\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/6223572311e4f102e8caa1a1548a0bb6.webm?t=1755598292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/6223572311e4f102e8caa1a1548a0bb6.mp4?t=1755598292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Thoughtful and Engaging Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the story of Dominic, a man with the unique power to eject blades from his wrists. After learning about missing people in his hometown, Dominic stumbles onto the underground plot that will change his life forever. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along his journey, Dominic teams up with outcasts of various flavors. What happens when they fight for the society that would scorn them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story about loneliness, responsibility, and what it really means to be your true self.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191550/extras/06cf2e8bfbb828c5b7787c2b804cd2c5.avif?t=1755598292\" width=720 height=242 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Violent, blood-pumping action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 playable characters with unique play styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >57 levels of ramping  difficulty</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Post-game challenges!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the S ratings by completing levels under a certain time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play every level as your favorite character!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardcore mode: Can you beat the whole game without dying?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed running</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more!</p></li></ul>",
